            >knowledge
          </span> in the age of <span
            class="font-semibold underline underline-offset-1 decoration-2 decoration-blue-400 dark:decoration-blue-600"
            >big data.</span
          >
        </h6>
        <h6 class="mt-2 text-primary text-base">
          Lately, I've been employing state-of-the-art <span
            class="font-semibold underline underline-offset-1 decoration-2 decoration-blue-400 dark:decoration-blue-600"
            >machine learning</span
          > techniques to accurately predict and detect malignant lung cancer in
          its early stages, thereby facilitating prevention and treatment assessment
          based on trustworthy and dependable datasets.
        </h6>
      </article>
    </div>

